1384
01:45:18,650 --> 01:45:19,650
What?

1385
01:45:21,358 --> 01:45:23,150
Holy shit.

1386
01:45:37,358 --> 01:45:42,275
<i>It has been and it remains
the U/North position...</i>

1387
01:45:42,442 --> 01:45:46,525
<i>... that this lawsuit is baseless
