1388
01:45:46,692 --> 01:45:50,775
Our reluctance to negotiate
was anchored by this belief...

1389
01:45:50,942 --> 01:45:56,108
...and reinforced by the plaintiffs' demand
for settlement...

1390
01:45:56,275 --> 01:45:58,817
