1393
01:46:07,525 --> 01:46:11,942
<i>You all have
a tentative proposal packet...</i>

1394
01:46:12,525 --> 01:46:16,483
<i>... which outlines the details,
but the bottom line is this:</i>

1395
01:46:16,692 --> 01:46:19,442
<i>Over the past several months
we had gotten word...</i>

1396
01:46:19,608 --> 01:46:22,942
...that the plaintiffs were
growing impatient...

1397
01:46:23,108 --> 01:46:26,942
