1504
01:52:12,858 --> 01:52:14,317
Sure.

1505
01:52:14,692 --> 01:52:17,483
Just stay close, okay?

1506
01:52:17,650 --> 01:52:18,858
Okay.

1507
01:53:29,442 --> 01:53:31,275
So, what are we doing?

1508
